{
  "translations": [
    { "resource_id": 149, "text": "The Shocking Event!" },
    { "resource_id": 149, "text": "What is the Shocking Event?" },
    {
      "resource_id": 149,
      "text": "And what can make you<a class=\"sup\"><sup>sg </sup></a>realize what the Shocking Event is?"
    },
    {
      "resource_id": 149,
      "text": "A day when mankind become like scattered moths,"
    },
    {
      "resource_id": 149,
      "text": "and the mountains become like tufted wool."
    },
    {
      "resource_id": 149,
      "text": "So, as for the one whose scales were heavy<sup foot_note=\"81493\">1</sup>—"
    },
    { "resource_id": 149, "text": "he is in a pleasant life." },
    {
      "resource_id": 149,
      "text": "But as for the one whose scales were light<a class=\"sup\"><sup>b </sup></a>—"
    },
    {
      "resource_id": 149,
      "text": "his home<sup foot_note=\"81494\">1</sup>is an Abyss."
    },
    {
      "resource_id": 149,
      "text": "And what can make you<a class=\"sup\"><sup>sg </sup></a>realize what it is?"
    },
    { "resource_id": 149, "text": "A raging fire." }
